re. He is a villainous scoundrel: avoid him as you would avoid fire, and do not allow him to enter the house under any pretext. I have wandered from my original subject. I have nothing else to say. Thou wilt give the letter to Michele.\r","standoffProperties":[{"id":"50e97c8f-b56e-4755-80bf-1210a09504c6","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":9,"value":"eb5c2755-f869-4ca7-8733-1c39b95bc7a0","text":"Buonarrot","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"ba1bb653-3d33-4ee4-9d24-58c6f4bacebe","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":14,"end":16,"value":"eb5c2755-f869-4ca7-8733-1c39b95bc7a0","text":"Th","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"7408012c-e52e-43da-8c41-ddef99f0a42f","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":105,"end":105,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","text":"","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"922c7073-3418-4932-954c-89533e529f6e","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":146,"end":146,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","text":"","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"6b1be912-782c-4fdb-9338-7f9b59422867","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":183,"end":183,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","text":"","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"8a4874ca-7efa-4040-9028-2d93091d4e00","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":203,"end":206,"value":"eb5c2755-f869-4ca7-8733-1c39b95bc7a0","text":"the","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"436cf8cc-af49-4ce3-a830-f33ab3c50488","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":209,"end":209,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","text":"","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"8d4c2ee4-8aac-4122-aff3-4fd164cc7622","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":223,"end":226,"value":"eb5c2755-f869-4ca7-8733-1c39b95bc7a0","text":"the","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"009b58fb-548d-44b9-b94d-581b32a5c349","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":280,"end":286,"valu